ia-helper (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Language filter for search: curated dropdown matching IA's mixed
    metadata conventions (MARC/ISO codes and names OR'd per language);
    composes with sorting, paging, and bulk downloads.
  * Mediatype and language filter changes now apply to the active
    search immediately.

 -- Joe Hallmark <joe.hallmark@gmail.com>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 18:00:00 +1200

ia-helper (1.2.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Grouped downloads view: one expander per item with aggregate
    progress and group pause/resume/cancel/open-folder.
  * Bulk downloads: download everything matching a search, collection,
    or uploader — survey with size confirmation, self-pacing queue
    feeder, restriction-aware, pausable/resumable, cancel propagates to
    the job's downloads, optional per-format filtering.

 -- Joe Hallmark <joe.hallmark@gmail.com>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +1200

